  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Joint Replacement Surgery - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_joint_replacement_surgery">Joint Replacement Surgery</xref>
 is a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_clinical_intervention">CLINICAL INTERVENTION</xref>
.  </p>
  <p>
There are two types of 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_joint_replacement_surgery">Joint Replacement Surgery</xref>
 referred to in the 
    <xref href="http://www.datadictionary.nhs.uk/data_dictionary/messages/clinical_content/overviews/national_joint_registry_data_set_overviews/national_joint_registry_data_set_introduction.asp"
            scope="external"
            format="html">National Joint Registry Data Set</xref>
:  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
Primary 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_joint_replacement_surgery">Joint Replacement Surgery</xref>
            </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
This uses 
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_implant">Implants</xref>
 made from metal, high density polyethylene or ceramic to replace a diseased or worn out joint and  </p>
  <ul>
      <li>
         <div>
            <p>
Revision 
                <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
                     keyref="business_definition_joint_replacement_surgery">Joint Replacement Surgery</xref>
            </p>
         </div>
      </li>
  </ul>
  <p>
This involves removing 
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_implant">Implants</xref>
 that were inserted during Primary 
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_joint_replacement_surgery">Joint Replacement Surgery</xref>
, and usually involves replacing them with new 
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_implant">Implants</xref>
.  </p>

